00:14:28,434 --> 00:14:30,674
called Fragment Time Boyfriend.

284
00:14:31,474 --> 00:14:32,554
Is it still going on?

285
00:14:33,434 --> 00:14:35,354
Yes, it is.

286
00:14:35,474 --> 00:14:37,474
