a few days ago.

287
00:14:38,354 --> 00:14:39,674
Would you mind showing it to me?

288
00:14:40,234 --> 00:14:42,434
Great, I'll send it to you tomorrow.

289
00:14:42,914 --> 00:14:43,474
Okay.

290
00:14:43,674 --> 00:14:44,474
Miss Lan.

291
00:14:45,594 --> 00:14:46,674
You came just in time.

292
00:14:52,594 --> 00:14:53,994
Let me introduce him to you.

293
00:14:54,514 --> 00:14:56,434
This is our new director
at Lansheng Investment,

294
00:14:56,554 --> 00:14:57,714
Pei Jun.

295
00:14:58,634 --> 00:15:00,234
This is An Ran from Gaishi Unparalleled.

296
00:15:00,714 --> 00:15:01,874
You guys get to know each other.

297
00:15:03,474 --> 00:15:04,194
Miss An.

298
00:15:17,354 --> 00:15:19,554
An Ran, if you need anything,

299
00:15:19,594 --> 00:15:20,914
just go directly to Mr. Pei.

300
00:15:21,354 --> 00:15:24,034
He is in charge of investment
in small and medium-sized enterprises.

301
00:15:25,954 --> 00:15:28,114
Miss An will have a cooperation with us.

302
00:15:28,154 --> 00:15:29,314
I hope you two work well.

303
00:15:29,434 --> 00:15:30,554
Don't worry, Miss Lan.

304
00:15:31,474 --> 00:15:32,354
Then I'll go in first.

305
00:15:32,434 --> 00:15:33,554
You two can talk.

306
00:15:42,794 --> 00:15:43,914
Ran.

307
00:15:47,554 --> 00:15:48,594
Long time no see.

308
00:15:49,648 --> 00:15:53,360
♪A sky full of stars
as bright as candles♪

309
00:15:53,360 --> 00:15:56,976
♪The breeze sings softly♪

310
00:15:56,976 --> 00:16:02,000
♪The moon dances alone
