314
00:16:11,920 --> 00:16:13,892
♪Recalling that past♪

315
00:16:14,160 --> 00:16:16,496
♪That certain scene♪

316
00:16:17,296 --> 00:16:21,184
♪I'm not good at expressing♪

317
00:16:21,184 --> 00:16:24,842
♪Companionship is a silent gift♪

318
00:16:24,842 --> 00:16:26,640
♪Brief embraces♪

319
00:16:26,640 --> 00:16:28,464
♪Long loneliness♪

320
00:16:29,114 --> 00:16:31,474
Mr. Pei, the discussion
is about to start.

321
00:16:31,594 --> 00:16:33,394
Please come in first.

322
00:16:35,632 --> 00:16:39,179
♪Your heart could belong only to me♪

323
00:16:39,728 --> 00:16:41,808
♪The one and only♪

324
00:16:43,634 --> 00:16:44,912
Why is your forehead burning?

325
00:16:46,834 --> 00:16:47,696
