330
00:16:54,714 --> 00:16:57,034
Examine your body with these forms.

331
00:17:09,994 --> 00:17:10,914
You're awake.

332
00:17:14,434 --> 00:17:15,834
We need to wait for the report.

333
00:17:16,432 --> 00:17:17,424
You rest for a while.

334
00:17:19,216 --> 00:17:20,674
Or let's not wait.

335
00:17:20,714 --> 00:17:22,154
Let's just go home.

336
00:17:22,154 --> 00:17:23,674
It's reassuring to know the result.

337
00:17:24,154 --> 00:17:25,034
Hang in there.

338
00:17:30,256 --> 00:17:32,914
What happened to you just now?

339
00:17:33,034 --> 00:17:34,674
Your looked bad.

340
00:17:37,354 --> 00:17:38,114
It's nothing.

341
00:17:44,194 --> 00:17:45,594
I don't like arguing.

342
00:17:47,314 --> 00:17:49,274
When I hear others arguing,

343
00:17:49,834 --> 00:17:50,864
I will get uncomfortable.

344
00:17:55,234 --> 00:17:58,074
It's okay
if you don't want to talk about it.

345
00:18:00,794 --> 00:18:01,994
Don't talk about me.

346
00:18:02,434 --> 00:18:03,314
Are you feeling better?

347
00:18:04,880 --> 00:18:06,434
I think so.

348
00:18:12,634 --> 00:18:13,394
Much better.

349
00:18:15,194 --> 00:18:16,034
Drink some water.

350
00:18:16,354 --> 00:18:17,434
Thanks.

351
00:18:17,834 --> 00:18:18,714
Take it slow.

352
00:18:33,194 --> 00:18:34,114
I'll go get the report.

353
00:18:35,474 --> 00:18:36,314
Okay.

354
00:18:36,754 --> 00:18:37,194
Wait here.

355
00:18:56,034 --> 00:18:57,154
You got it?

356
00:19:05,808 --> 00:19:08,154
(Huikang Hospital HCG Test Report)

357
00:19:08,154 --> 00:19:10,954
Human chorionic gonadotropin.

358
00:19:11,314 --> 00:19:12,274
What is this?

359
00:19:19,312 --> 00:19:22,096
(HCG test: commonly known as
pregnancy test.)

360
00:19:26,864 --> 00:19:28,314
Well, what's going on?

361
00:19:28,314 --> 00:19:30,096
A pregnancy test?

362
00:19:30,096 --> 00:19:31,274
How could it be?

363
00:19:46,594 --> 00:19:48,434
That night after the school alumni...

364
00:19:53,194 --> 00:19:54,434
What happened that night?

365
00:19:55,434 --> 00:19:56,714
That night,

366
00:19:57,234 --> 00:19:58,674
didn't anything happen, did it?

367
00:20:00,074 --> 00:20:00,994
Are you sure?

368
00:20:23,834 --> 00:20:25,154
I was drunk.

369
00:20:25,154 --> 00:20:26,314
We're adults.

370
00:20:26,314 --> 00:20:27,714
Don't make such a big deal of it.

371
00:20:29,354 --> 00:20:30,194
I wasn't drunk.

372
00:20:46,114 --> 00:20:46,954
Seat belt.

373
00:21:17,314 --> 00:21:18,314
Are you okay?

374
00:21:22,594 --> 00:21:23,234
Do you need me?

375
00:21:23,314 --> 00:21:24,634
No need.

376
00:21:27,994 --> 00:21:28,834
Your medicine.

377
00:21:33,554 --> 00:21:34,834
Thank you for today.

378
00:21:35,314 --> 00:21:35,914
Good night.

379
00:21:36,314 --> 00:21:37,034
Good night.

380
00:22:32,114 --> 00:22:32,914
See you.

381
00:22:33,394 --> 00:22:34,394
Thank you all.

382
00:22:41,994 --> 00:22:44,314
Hi, I really like your painting.

383
00:22:45,154 --> 00:22:46,554
Can we make friends?

384
00:22:46,954 --> 00:22:47,994
My name is Pei Jun.

385
00:22:48,794 --> 00:22:49,834
My name is An Ran.

386
00:22:58,554 --> 00:22:59,634
(It often happens.)

387
00:23:00,114 --> 00:23:01,554
(When we fall in love,)

388
00:23:01,994 --> 00:23:03,280
(we will be at a loss.)

389
00:23:04,994 --> 00:23:07,314
(Dopamine pushes us
beyond our comfort zone.)

390
00:23:08,794 --> 00:23:10,754
(But at certain moments,)

391
00:23:12,594 --> 00:23:14,114
(we realize all our confidence)

392
00:23:14,874 --> 00:23:15,714
(is just an illusion.)

393
00:23:16,994 --> 00:23:19,194
(Advancing or retreating,)

394
00:23:20,514 --> 00:23:22,594
(there's no proper distance.)

395
00:24:29,474 --> 00:24:31,194
What am I doing?

396
00:25:47,034 --> 00:25:48,794
Get in the car. I can give you a lift.

397
00:25:50,634 --> 00:25:52,034
I'm taking the bus today.

398
00:25:52,154 --> 00:25:53,634
I'm going to the other direction.

399
00:25:53,794 --> 00:25:55,154
So I won't be going with you.

400
00:26:14,714 --> 00:26:15,354
Pei Jun.

401
00:26:15,834 --> 00:26:17,234
Mengyao, enter from that side.

402
00:26:17,434 --> 00:26:18,194
Okay.

403
00:26:25,514 --> 00:26:27,314
I ordered your favorite latte.

404
00:26:27,314 --> 00:26:27,834
Is that okay?

405
00:26:28,154 --> 00:26:29,354
Yes, thank you.

406
00:26:31,834 --> 00:26:33,914
You haven't changed at all
after all these years.

407
00:26:34,074 --> 00:26:34,954
Thank you.

408
00:26:35,514 --> 00:26:36,674
But you're completely different.

409
00:26:37,314 --> 00:26:38,914
You used to follow Ran around.

410
00:26:39,274 --> 00:26:40,434
After a trip to France,

411
00:26:40,434 --> 00:26:41,514
you're a different person now.

412
00:26:41,914 --> 00:26:42,674
Yes.

413
00:26:43,034 --> 00:26:45,154
When I just arrived in France,
I felt awfully out of it.

414
00:26:45,394 --> 00:26:47,954
I didn't expect
I would feel the same way at home.

415
00:26:48,434 --> 00:26:50,194
Yes, I felt the same when I went abroad.

416
00:26:50,714 --> 00:26:52,034
Life abroad seems easy.

417
00:26:52,074 --> 00:26:53,314
But actually, I felt so stressed.

418
00:26:54,314 --> 00:26:55,514
When did you come back?

419
00:26:55,554 --> 00:26:56,674
I came back recently.

420
00:26:57,794 --> 00:26:59,674
When I just walked around,

421
00:26:59,714 --> 00:27:02,554
I saw the restaurants
we used to go to together.

422
00:27:02,954 --> 00:27:03,674
They're still there.

423
00:27:03,714 --> 00:27:05,274
And I started thinking about those times

424
00:27:05,914 --> 00:27:08,074
when life was so simple and happy.

425
00:27:08,634 --> 00:27:10,314
Time flies.

426
00:27:10,554 --> 00:27:11,920
Back then, An Ran and I...

427
00:27:18,234 --> 00:27:18,954
Pei Jun.

428
00:27:19,674 --> 00:27:23,034
So why did you break up with An Ran?

429
00:27:24,674 --> 00:27:25,714
Didn't she tell you?

430
00:27:25,834 --> 00:27:26,834
No.

431
00:27:26,914 --> 00:27:29,554
She didn't tell me when I asked her.

432
00:27:30,714 --> 00:27:33,274
You two were a perfect match.

433
00:27:33,314 --> 00:27:34,434
So many people envied you.

434
00:27:34,434 --> 00:27:35,714
You two were the model couple.

435
00:27:36,434 --> 00:27:39,194
How could it end up in a breakup?

436
00:27:43,074 --> 00:27:44,794
It was probably
because of some small things.

437
00:27:45,074 --> 00:27:47,034
Maybe we both didn't understand love

438
00:27:47,434 --> 00:27:48,314
at that time.

439
00:27:48,554 --> 00:27:49,914
So it ended up that way.

440
00:27:51,034 --> 00:27:53,514
But I've thought a lot abroad.

441
00:27:53,954 --> 00:27:56,112
I was too hasty in my decision.

442
00:27:57,314 --> 00:27:58,554
I made a mistake.

443
00:27:59,154 --> 00:28:01,776
Love is complicated.

444
00:28:03,634 --> 00:28:06,274
So, what are your plans?

445
00:28:09,554 --> 00:28:10,514
To be honest,

446
00:28:10,554 --> 00:28:12,954
I came back for Ran.

447
00:28:14,434 --> 00:28:15,714
I want to apologize to her in person

448
00:28:15,794 --> 00:28:16,914
and win her back.

449
00:28:20,194 --> 00:28:22,514
Mengyao, can you help me?

450
00:28:24,674 --> 00:28:25,554
Sure.

451
00:28:30,194 --> 00:28:31,274
Peng, do you think

452
00:28:31,434 --> 00:28:33,794
this scene might be a bit dull?

453
00:28:37,034 --> 00:28:39,434
I want to redo the lighting

454
00:28:39,634 --> 00:28:42,034
and add some new elements in the scene.

455
00:28:42,794 --> 00:28:43,674
But,

456
00:28:43,914 --> 00:28:45,554
I haven't figured out how to do it yet.

457
00:28:45,674 --> 00:28:47,714
No worries. You can do it.

458
00:28:49,434 --> 00:28:52,074
By the way, how do you feel
about working with Yaoyao?

459
00:28:54,154 --> 00:28:55,194
She's super talented.

460
00:28:55,394 --> 00:28:56,554
Her painting is stylish.

461
00:28:56,794 --> 00:28:58,794
I've seen her new character design.

462
00:28:58,954 --> 00:29:01,434
I want to modify our old design

463
00:29:01,794 --> 00:29:02,794
to match hers.

464
00:29:02,914 --> 00:29:04,074
Good.

465
00:29:04,554 --> 00:29:07,274
I didn't expect Bai Mengyao
to get used to this job so quickly.

466
00:29:07,314 --> 00:29:08,554
Let's go.

467
00:29:12,314 --> 00:29:13,674
It's time to find Yan Yue.

468
00:29:20,914 --> 00:29:23,674
I made an appointment with a client.
You go by yourself.

469
00:29:25,834 --> 00:29:26,954
Which client?

470
00:29:29,834 --> 00:29:31,434
I'll call the client.

471
00:29:31,634 --> 00:29:32,816
We'll talk about it later.

472
00:29:34,794 --> 00:29:36,434
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

473
00:29:56,194 --> 00:29:57,554
What are you reading?

474
00:30:02,114 --> 00:30:03,354
How about dinner tonight?

475
00:30:03,434 --> 00:30:04,754
We can talk about something.

476
00:30:05,554 --> 00:30:06,434
About what?

477
00:30:08,754 --> 00:30:09,954
An Ran said she wanted

478
00:30:09,954 --> 00:30:11,914
to establish a long-term cooperation
with you.

479
00:30:12,434 --> 00:30:13,674
You think...

480
00:30:15,314 --> 00:30:16,034
Let her talk to me.

481
00:30:16,816 --> 00:30:18,154
Wait a minute.

482
00:30:20,394 --> 00:30:21,434
She brought it up.

483
00:30:21,834 --> 00:30:22,674
I didn't understand.

484
00:30:24,194 --> 00:30:25,904
How about I call her over?

485
00:30:27,274 --> 00:30:28,554
We talk about it tonight?

486
00:30:28,880 --> 00:30:29,794
Please.

487
00:30:52,914 --> 00:30:53,936
Hello, Miss Lan.

488
00:30:55,554 --> 00:30:56,354
Really?

489
00:30:56,914 --> 00:30:58,914
Okay, we'll definitely prepare well.

490
00:30:59,874 --> 00:31:00,514
That's great.

491
00:31:07,440 --> 00:31:08,304
Friends,

492
00:31:09,234 --> 00:31:11,152
I have good news to tell you.

493
00:31:12,474 --> 00:31:13,874
Miss Lan of Lansheng Investment

494
00:31:13,874 --> 00:31:16,208
is very optimistic
about our Fragment Time Boyfriend.

495
00:31:16,954 --> 00:31:20,394
She gave us the opportunity
to make a proposal to Lansheng.

496
00:31:23,674 --> 00:31:24,834
But,

497
00:31:25,194 --> 00:31:26,634
the senior executives of Lansheng

498
00:31:26,674 --> 00:31:28,554
are worried about our ability

499
00:31:28,554 --> 00:31:30,074
to independently develop games.

500
00:31:30,514 --> 00:31:31,914
Why?

501
00:31:32,434 --> 00:31:34,794
Because we don't have any mature works.

502
00:31:35,154 --> 00:31:36,034
So,

503
00:31:36,194 --> 00:31:38,674
I proposed a plan to Miss Lan.

504
00:31:38,834 --> 00:31:41,034
During the time
we're preparing our proposal,

505
00:31:41,074 --> 00:31:43,954
we'll make a demo.

506
00:31:44,074 --> 00:31:45,794
In this way,

507
00:31:45,834 --> 00:31:47,674
our proposal will be more compelling.

508
00:31:52,074 --> 00:31:53,554
Good idea.

509
00:31:53,714 --> 00:31:55,834
So we don't have to show a presentation.

510
00:31:56,074 --> 00:31:57,514
We make something

511
00:31:57,554 --> 00:31:59,034
to prove our strength.

512
00:32:00,274 --> 00:32:02,154
Good for you.

513
00:32:03,434 --> 00:32:04,434
Thank you.

514
00:32:05,514 --> 00:32:08,074
But this demo,

515
00:32:08,274 --> 00:32:09,554
four boyfriends,

516
00:32:09,714 --> 00:32:11,914
apart from drawing,
we need to dub it, right?

517
00:32:14,554 --> 00:32:15,954
It's a problem.

518
00:32:16,314 --> 00:32:18,434
Didn't you want to work with Heisha?

519
00:32:18,634 --> 00:32:20,354
Yan Yue can help.

520
00:32:35,514 --> 00:32:37,474
I don't think so.

521
00:32:37,754 --> 00:32:40,634
We've troubled Mr. Heisha so many times.

522
00:32:40,994 --> 00:32:41,914
No worries.

523
00:32:41,994 --> 00:32:43,874
We can pay him.

524
00:32:43,914 --> 00:32:44,994
To express our sincerity,

525
00:32:44,994 --> 00:32:45,994
how about giving him shares?

526
00:32:48,274 --> 00:32:50,234
I can help with the dubbing.

527
00:32:51,754 --> 00:32:53,104
Who said I wouldn't do it?

528
00:32:55,874 --> 00:32:57,394
Mr. Heisha is here.

529
00:32:57,914 --> 00:32:59,154
I don't need the shares.

530
00:32:59,514 --> 00:33:01,394
But I have a condition.

531
00:33:02,114 --> 00:33:04,994
Miss An is in charge of my dubbing work.

532
00:33:07,114 --> 00:33:10,634
After all, Miss An is my fan.

533
00:33:10,994 --> 00:33:12,434
She knows my dubbing best.

534
00:33:17,474 --> 00:33:18,514
Of course.

535
00:33:19,514 --> 00:33:20,754
What about one more condition?

536
00:33:21,034 --> 00:33:22,354
No dubbing in the morning.

537
00:33:23,834 --> 00:33:24,754
That's not necessary.

538
00:33:31,994 --> 00:33:33,394
We must be confident, right?

539
00:33:33,474 --> 00:33:35,234
Alright, I will do a good job.

540
00:33:35,274 --> 00:33:35,994
Miss An, bye.

541
00:33:36,034 --> 00:33:36,914
Bye.

542
00:33:36,994 --> 00:33:37,754
See you, Miss An.

543
00:33:37,874 --> 00:33:38,514
Bye.

544
00:33:39,394 --> 00:33:39,914
See you.

545
00:33:39,994 --> 00:33:41,034
- Bye.
- No problem.

546
00:33:46,394 --> 00:33:46,954
Go home?

547
00:33:49,712 --> 00:33:51,120
I'm going to the supermarket.

548
00:33:51,874 --> 00:33:52,874
You go home first.

549
00:34:04,554 --> 00:34:05,354
You go home.

550
00:34:30,834 --> 00:34:33,840
It's raining so heavily.
I have no umbrella.

551
00:36:10,274 --> 00:36:11,194
Ran.

552
00:36:11,994 --> 00:36:13,194
Sorry, I'm late.

553
00:36:13,314 --> 00:36:13,834
That's okay.

554
00:36:14,274 --> 00:36:15,434
It's raining heavily.

555
00:36:15,914 --> 00:36:16,834
Are you hungry?

556
00:36:17,554 --> 00:36:19,314
I booked a table at a restaurant.

557
00:36:19,594 --> 00:36:20,114
Okay.

558
00:36:20,474 --> 00:36:20,994
Let's go.

559
00:36:55,641 --> 00:37:00,249
♪The movie told an undulating
and complicated story♪

560
00:37:02,522 --> 00:37:07,961
♪And there is only one possibility
between us♪

561
00:37:09,731 --> 00:37:14,521
♪We entangle ourselves in love♪

562
00:37:15,490 --> 00:37:18,105
♪What are you thinking about♪

563
00:37:18,105 --> 00:37:21,849
♪Where should I stand♪

564
00:37:21,849 --> 00:37:23,865
♪From the strange to the familiar♪

565
00:37:23,865 --> 00:37:26,489
♪From the familiar to the strange,
it's an inevitable part of love♪

566
00:37:26,489 --> 00:37:29,530
